{"id":601457,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/【立此存照】把人家书名都给改了/","date":"2018-12-12T09:42:34Z","modified":"2018-12-12T09:45:55Z","title":"【立此存照】把人家书名都给改了","content":"<p>12月12日，女作家上官乱发推称，自己在2017年上市的书《<a href=\"https://book.douban.com/subject/27043857/\">这样走，才能看到台湾</a>》在京东等自营店（手机app检索）被强制修改了书名，将“台湾”替换成了“台湾地区”。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">刚发现，京东上我的书名被改了 <a href=\"https://t.co/XYaB0XPQBR\">pic.twitter.com/XYaB0XPQBR</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 上官乱 (@shangguanluan) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/shangguanluan/status/1072725688233283584?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">December 12, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-601458\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DuMWT6LUcAIGZu_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DuMWT6LUcAIGZu_.jpg 675w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DuMWT6LUcAIGZu_-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/DuMWT6LUcAIGZu_-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>经检索发现，此情况并非孤例，京东app上大量社科类书籍，均被替换了书名，加上了“地区”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-601459\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/IMAGE-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"930\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/IMAGE-1.jpg 1125w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/IMAGE-1-145x300.jpg 145w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/IMAGE-1-768x1587.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/IMAGE-1-495x1024.jpg 495w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%86%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4%e